<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Invitation to Football Match</title>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<style type="text/css">
		/* Responsive styles */
		@media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
			.container {
				width: 100% !important;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
		<h1 style="text-align: center;">You're invited to a football match!</h1>
		<p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
		<p>You have been invited to play in a football match against the team "<%= opponentTeam %>". We hope you can join us for an exciting match!</p>
		<p>Please click on the link below to accept or decline the invitation:</p>
		<p><a href="<%= acceptLink %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Accept Invitation</a></p>
		<p>Thank you for being a part of our football community. We hope to see you on the pitch soon!</p>
		<p>Best regards,</p>
		<p>The Football Team</p>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
